            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "27歲前台軍女輔導長  投身色情平台拍片實戰男友  轉行年薪火速暴增",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"27歲前台軍女輔導長  投身色情平台拍片實戰男友  轉行年薪火速暴增\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f68f335bdfae8346b24609670b58a8ec/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031222423528772.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">27歲前台軍女輔導長  投身色情平台拍片實戰男友  轉行年薪火速暴增</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>現年27歲的前台軍八軍團女輔導長「內內」，因為兩年前和男友在營區拍攝性愛影片，之後遭到開除，及後她轉當成人平台SWAG直播主。經過兩年時間，原本不脫的她近期突破尺度，在直播間和男友「實戰」，不單在房間床上，更在浴室進行，不止上空展現好身材，還拍攝大尺度影片！\n\n</p>\n<p>家人勸別「跟人家去做露屁股的」\n\n</p>\n<p>事實上，內內先前談到轉當成人平台直播主，家人起初並不知情，家人得知後更是難以接受，勸她「不要跟人家去做露屁股的」，但她認為這也是一個工作，不讓外界眼光影響自己。她不認為有什麼不妥：「我想說也是一個工作，畢竟我也沒給人家碰到什麼的。」\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-entertainment/3436324/%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%8A%E6%82%A0%E4%BA%9E%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E7%AA%81%E6%99%92%E5%A9%9A%E7%85%A7%E6%89%8B%E6%8D%A7%E9%AE%AE%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9C%E7%AC%91%E6%83%B9%E5%85%A8%E7%B6%B2%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-23%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%95%E9%80%80AV%E7%95%8C\">三上悠亞宣佈結婚？突晒婚照手捧鮮花甜笑惹全網熱議   23年宣布引退AV界</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133808/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內今年27歲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1227084d7af5f8edc48a9d7deff85f44/2025-03/SS1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內今年27歲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133809/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本身為台軍女輔導長，但兩年前內內於營中和男友的私密影片被流出，最終被開除。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/58b984b4ac86a37f41d0b009978a65b9/2025-03/Q2_3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本身為台軍女輔導長，但兩年前內內於營中和男友的私密影片被流出，最終被開除。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133810/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"之後內內加盟成人平台。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/23d4bca3ab776786822417738876094d/2025-03/Q3_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        之後內內加盟成人平台。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133811/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內於成人平台轉當直播主。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0793eb123e014f1ea6da424a122acba8/2025-03/Q4_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內於成人平台轉當直播主。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133812/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內年薪就此暴升5倍。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/30aa357fc9ddbdd4ac414af932329cee/2025-03/Q5_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內年薪就此暴升5倍。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133813/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內之前堅持不脫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/310ac419109d33dae634df88ca077dfb/2025-03/Q6_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內之前堅持不脫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133814/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內最近拍攝大尺度影片，和男友實戰！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5191d7dc50c86529e265b7b05b18cf6c/2025-03/Q7_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內最近拍攝大尺度影片，和男友實戰！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133815/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內越來越大膽。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/377bc4167d935e1bb795651be5f21909/2025-03/Q8_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內越來越大膽。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133825/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內身材修長。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7ee6bcfb7f98351d975289613dccf1cd/2025-03/R1_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內身材修長。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133826/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"內內都有端裝的時候。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8520fdc714dffd517d11aabcd2e104b3/2025-03/R2_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        內內都有端裝的時候。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>另外內內也表示，私密影片流出後家人都知道實際情況。事發當時她選擇直接消失一段時間，避免面對過多壓力：「因為我覺得我沒辦法承受他們給我的關心。」雖然同場嘉賓小鐘安慰「這也不是妳的錯」，但她也承認：「我在不對的地方是事實。」轉當主播主後，有關公司證實內內合約價值為台北市蛋黃區一間套房，年薪比當軍人時爆增5倍。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-entertainment/3434922/26%E6%AD%B2%E6%9A%97%E9%BB%91%E6%9F%AF%E4%BD%B3%E5%AC%BF%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A-%E5%A4%A717%E6%AD%B2%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AFAV%E7%94%B7%E5%84%AA\">26歲「暗黑柯佳嬿」宣布結婚 大17歲老公身分曝光 竟是AV男優！</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
